me.elrod.pureio

Class UnsafePerformIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.elrod.pureio.UnsafePerformIO

  • public class UnsafePerformIO
extends java.lang.Object
    A compatibility interpreter for our free IO monads to make them do things in a way that a typical Java environment might expect. You could implement your own to do cooler, better, things.
